#: ../../../arch/x86/amd-hfi.rst:37
msgid ""
"The ``amd_hfi`` driver delivers the operating system a performance and "
"energy efficiency capability data for each CPU in the system. The scheduler "
"can use the ranking data from the HFI driver to make task placement "
"decisions."
msgstr ""

